data.description: Immaculate home in Homestead at Riversbend! Over 4400 sq feet & 3 levels of living space. Gourmet kitchen with double oven, gas cooktop & island opens to family room & breakfast room. Large primary suite with sitting area & 2 walk in closets. Finished LL with exercise room, rec room, flex room and  bath. Spacious deck with retractable awning overlooks private yard with fire pit. Additional features:  3 car garage, smart irrigation system, underground pet fence, new water heater, new LVP flooring in LL, new gutters with guards, new landscape lighting, new fridge. Cul-de-sac lot.  Low HOA. KINGS SCHOOLS!
